Energetically the calculation amounts to a Landau expansion. Only terms quadratic and cubic in the
order parameter S2 are considered. The critical spontaneous curvature makes the cubic term vanish.
To lowest order, the amplitude s4 of the fourth
Legendre polynomial is proportional to S2 . The associated energy varies as s24 and is thus irrelevant
for the present purpose.

